Final submission checklist

23. Check your file names

The brief gives the naming rules:
	•	Proposal: Task1_Proposal_[Registration number]_[Surname]_[First letter of first name]
	•	Design docs: Task1_DesignDocs_[Document name]_[Registration number]_[Surname]_[First letter of first name]  ￼

24. Save as PDFs

The proposal and design documents must be saved as PDFs for submission.  ￼

25. Add citations

The brief says any work that is not your own must be identified with appropriate citations.  ￼

